text: James John Lacey (22 November 1887 – 9 April 1956) was an Australian rules footballer who played with South Melbourne and Richmond in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * * Category:1887 births Category:1956 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Sydney Swans players Category:Richmond Football Club players
